description: The Haute Potato is bringing you all new ways to enjoy the potatoes you love! Gourmet potatoes, from the classic to the globally inspired, are bringing you real comfort cuisine you can sink your teeth into. With their Stuffed Baked Potatoes, Chili Batonettes, Southern Smoke Nachos, and more, The Haute Potato is cooking up some creative dishes that  you're sure to love!
name: The Haute Potato
